div.div:
- for illustration, assume fund f1 and f2 provided 60% and 40% resUSD liquidity to collateralize resBTC minting
- also assume protocol decided 110% is the collateral ratio to underwrite at when minting
- also assume fee is 10%
- increase f1 and f2's debt balance, by 6 * .9 = 5.4 and 3.6 resUSD
; liquidator will watch for liquidations, eg liquidate the fund / account when collateral ratio < 105%
- fees deduct here
- respond ok
